# ExamSpark Credit Economy Rule (v2)

Full spec: [`CREDIT_ECONOMY.md`](CREDIT_ECONOMY.md)

## Core Principle

- Users see **Credits only** — never rupee amounts for AI actions
- Internal (backend only): **1 Credit ≈ ₹0.15** charged-value — never in UI
- Most features are **session/feature-based**. **Exception:** Record + Audio Upload = **per-minute** (1/min, round up, max 180); YouTube stays banded

