## Plans (v2.2 — Jul 15, 2026)

| Plan | Credits/mo | Unlocks |
|------|------------|---------|
| Guest (no account) | 1 free Ask only | No credits ledger |
| Free | 50 | Ask AI, PDF, Photo/Diagram (credits). Audio locked. Groups = 0 |
| ₹199 | 1,500 | More credits. Join 1 Group. Audio still locked |
| ₹499 | 3,500 | + Audio recording/upload. Join 3 Groups |
| ₹999 | 8,000 | Full access. Join 6 Groups |
| Teacher ₹1999 | 16,000 | Bulk record + B2B tools |

Paid plans get **their** monthly credits only — Free’s 50 is **not** added on top.

